reviewText: I love Bev Bos!  If you work with children ages 2-8, this is a must see!

This should be required viewing for anyone working or running a daycare or preschool. Although, I wouldn't follow all of Bev Bos' recommendations her love of children and passion for encouraging children to be themselves is important for all educators and caregivers out there. Her ability to engage children in creative activities and remind us of the importance of freedom at such a young age is critical.
